title: Bobby Shmurda Cashes out on a new Rolex
author: Avianne Jewelers
description: Joe Avianne and Bobby Shmurda chop it while he is fresh out. Bobby drops a couple stacks on some new Avianne Water. Enjoy more love, power, and respect!
